snippet.title: Undead Citadel - Teaser
snippet.description:
More info on http://www.undeadcitadel.com

Undead Citadel is an action-packed title exclusively built for VR, focused on physics driven close/ranged medieval combat with real-life movements, where the player can explore a visually stunning fantasy universe threatened by undead annihilation.
